𝐇𝐨𝐰 𝐆𝐫𝐚𝐟𝐚𝐧𝐚 𝐕𝐢𝐬𝐮𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐳𝐞𝐬 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬

𝐆𝐫𝐚𝐟𝐚𝐧𝐚 turns raw Prometheus data into real-time dashboards — making complex metrics easy to read and act upon.

Benefits of Grafana:
✅ Custom dashboards for infrastructure, app, or business metrics
✅ Supports multiple data sources (Prometheus, Loki, Elastic, etc.)
✅ Alerting & sharing built right in
✅ Beautiful, interactive visualization

In short:
Prometheus collects. Grafana visualizes.
Together, they create complete observability.
